Download tableau, create acc for free, Go to the workbook that the class has given, download it and open it with Tableau public

Note: There must be default one/ more values in either ros/cols inorder to be saved.

Drag the latitude to row and longtiude to the column.

Drag the country Dimension to the map.

In measures, drag the Co2 emissions to color button. Co2 emmisions for each country is displayed. Change the color to Orange.
Filter by Year - . drag year dim to the filter box, and select the list of years for which the Co2 emissions are to be represented.
You can select single value list which filters by one year at a time.
